overview:
Dominic is a creative entrepreneur and business development professional.

Dominic runs Business Development and Sales for Curebit, a Y-Combinator backed start-up that focuses on building impactful social referral systems for top Internet Retailers.

Dominic received Global recognition as CEO of GarmentValet.com by winning the Global Student Entrepreneurship Award in 2008. The prestigious award was presented by Kaufmann Foundation and Entrepreneur’s Organization. At the time, Dominic was enrolled at Northeastern University where he holds a BS in Business Administration and Technological Entrepreneurship.

GarmentValet.com is a web based consumer services company that provides simplicity and convenience to all its customers; a PeaPod of Laundry & Dry Cleaning. Dominic is still involved as a Co-Founder/Shareholder and Advisor.

Dominic has deep experience in creative business strategy and hands-on execution.
